# Single-line comment test
# This is a single-line comment
አስተዋውቅ ስም = "ግእዝ"  # Inline comment
ማተም ስም

/* Multi-line comment test
   This is a multi-line comment
   It can span multiple lines
   and contains various content */
አስተዋውቅ አድሜ = 25
ማተም አድሜ

/* Another multi-line comment
   with mixed content:
   - Numbers: 123, 456
   - Strings: "hello", "world"
   - Amharic: ሰላም, እንደምን አለህ? */
አስተዋውቅ ዝርዝር = [1, 2, 3]
ማተም ዝርዝር

# Mixed comments test
አስተዋውቅ ቁጥር = 42  # Single-line after code
ማተም ቁጥር

/* 
   Large multi-line comment
   This comment demonstrates:
   1. Multiple lines
   2. Various formatting
   3. Code documentation
*/
አስተዋውቅ ውጤት = ቁጥር("100")
ማተም "ውጤት: " + ውጤት

# Final test
ማተም "All comment types working!"
